summary: Changes the guards of the mod ClosedBorderGates in order to make them Requiem compatible.
descriptionHtml:
If you want to use the mod ClosedBorderGates by Thicketford with Requiem you will notice that the guards are very easy to kill. I requiemfied them.

You of course need the original mod by Thicketford:

www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/44278/?

Concerning the load order... Just load my patch after ClosedBorderGates and Requiem - ClosedBorderGates itself can be everywhere... Before or after Requiem...
author: FleischHals
